'''TT-9''' was a [[Multi-Troop Transport/Legends|Multi-Troop Transport]] in the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]] [[Trade Federation Droid Army/Legends|Droid Army]] around [[32 BBY/Legends|32 BBY]].

TT-9 was designated as an auxiliary mobilization supply transport during the [[Invasion of Naboo/Legends|Invasion of Naboo]], and coordinated with the orbital [[Lucrehulk-class battleship/Legends|Droid Control Ship]] over [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]] to assign [[Single Trooper Aerial Platform/Legends|Single Trooper Aerial Platforms]] to particular areas of the occupation zone. TT-9 was conveyed to the planet's surface via a [[C-9979 landing craft/Legends|C-9979 landing craft]], and almost ran down [[Qui-Gon Jinn/Legends|Qui-Gon Jinn]] and [[Jar Jar Binks/Legends|Jar Jar Binks]] as it drove through the forest close to [[Lake Paonga/Legends|Lake Paonga]].

